com.nttdocomo.ui
Interface MediaData

All Superinterfaces:
MediaResource
public interface MediaData
extends MediaResource

This defines media data. This media data interface is used to define reusable data.
Media data is obtained using a method of MediaManager class. The type of class object to be returned is implementation dependent. As a media data interface it does not have a method for handling data.

See Also:
MediaManager
